        <hl1>THE MARKETS: CURRENCIES</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Yen hits three-week high against dollar; other international exchange rates noted (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>YEN RALLIES. The yen hit a three-week high against the dollar on speculation that the Bank of Japan might abandon its zero interest rate policy. In New York, the dollar traded at 106.73 yen, down from 108.70 on Thursday.</p>
      </block>
